## Entering Mode

### Enter Search mode (scrollback)

- <https://wezterm.org/scrollback.html#scrolling-without-a-scrollbar>
- `<C-S-f>` or Command-F

### Enter Yank(Copy) mode

- <https://wezterm.org/copymode.html#key-assignments>
- `<C-S-x>`

### Enter Quick Select Mode

- https://wezterm.org/quickselect.html
- `<C-S-SPC>`
- Alacritty 의 Vi 모드 진입과 동등.

